"title": "2054: Jesus Christ, mind of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2054",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The centre of Jesus Christ's thought, understanding and motivation, characterised by a total dedication to God. Christians are called upon to have the same mind as Christ.</p>\n<h2>The intellectual capacity of Jesus Christ's mind</h2>\n<h3>In childhood</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:47\">LUK 2:47</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:40\">LUK 2:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:52\">LUK 2:52</a></p>\n<h3>In adulthood</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:15\">JHN 7:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:28\">MAT 7:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:54\">MAT 13:54</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:2\">MRK 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:22\">MRK 1:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:32\">LUK 4:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:18\">MRK 11:18</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's mind was pure</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:26\">HEB 7:26</a></strong> <em>The purity of Jesus Christ's mind is declared by his words and actions and by his oneness with God.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:35\">LUK 1:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:30\">JHN 10:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:15\">HEB 4:15</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of Jesus Christ's use of his mind</h2>\n<h3>In overcoming temptation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:4\">MAT 4:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:4\">LUK 4:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:3\">DEU 8:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:42\">MAT 27:42</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:32\">MRK 15:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:37\">LUK 23:37</a></p>\n<h3>Against opposition</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:18-Matt22:22\">MAT 22:18–22:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:15-Mark12:17\">MRK 12:15–12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:22-Luke20:26\">LUK 20:22–20:26</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's mind is more than intellect</h2>\n<h3>His thinking is supported by prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:12-Luke6:13\">LUK 6:12–6:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:16\">LUK 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:41-Luke22:43\">LUK 22:41–22:43</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:39\">MAT 26:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:35-Mark14:36\">MRK 14:35–14:36</a></p>\n<h3>His thinking is tempered by understanding</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2\">ISA 11:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:35-Matt9:36\">MAT 9:35–9:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:22\">LUK 4:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:24-John2:25\">JHN 2:24–2:25</a></p>\n<h3>His mind experiences anguish</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:27\">JHN 12:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:38\">MAT 26:38</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:34\">MRK 14:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:46\">MAT 27:46</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:34\">MRK 15:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:1\">PSA 22:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:49-Luke12:50\">LUK 12:49–12:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:44\">LUK 22:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:21\">JHN 13:21</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's mind is extraordinary</h2>\n<h3>He has unusual insight</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:8\">MRK 2:8</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:4\">MAT 9:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:22\">LUK 5:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:25\">MAT 12:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:17\">LUK 11:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:8\">LUK 6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:47\">LUK 9:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:47-John1:48\">JHN 1:47–1:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:17-John4:18\">JHN 4:17–4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:4\">JHN 11:4</a></p>\n<h3>He understands the future</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:31\">MRK 8:31</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:21\">MAT 16:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:22\">LUK 9:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:21\">MAT 26:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:18\">MRK 14:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:34\">LUK 22:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:37\">LUK 22:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:12\">ISA 53:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:14\">JHN 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:49-John4:50\">JHN 4:49–4:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:33\">JHN 13:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:4\">JHN 18:4</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's mind did not know all things</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:10\">MAT 8:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:9\">LUK 7:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:21\">MRK 9:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:32\">MRK 13:32</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's strength of mind made him resolute</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:51\">LUK 9:51</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:14\">MAT 27:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:5\">MRK 15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:6\">JHN 6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:27\">JHN 12:27</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's mind was not always understood</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:32\">MRK 9:32</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:45\">LUK 9:45</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:21-Mark3:22\">MRK 3:21–3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:50\">LUK 2:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:34\">LUK 18:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:10\">JHN 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:27\">JHN 8:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:16\">JHN 12:16</a></p>\n<h2>Christians should have the same mind as Christ</h2>\n<h3>In his attitude</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:1\">1PE 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:16\">1CO 2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:13\">ISA 40:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:5\">PHP 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:8\">PHP 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2-Col2:3\">COL 2:2–2:3</a></p>\n<h3>In his knowledge of Scripture</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:28-Matt7:29\">MAT 7:28–7:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:29\">MAT 22:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:47\">LUK 2:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:27\">LUK 24:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:39\">JHN 5:39</a></p>\n<h3>In his awareness of God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:16\">JHN 8:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:28\">JHN 8:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:55\">JHN 8:55</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:10-John14:11\">JHN 14:10–14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:1\">JHN 17:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:6\">JHN 17:6</a></p>\n<h3>In the love in which Jesus Christ's mind is exercised</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:42\">LUK 11:42</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:23\">JHN 14:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:2\">1CO 13:2</a></p>",
